*  枠の作り方：BLOCK
    SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF BLOCK B1.
    PARAMETERS : A TYPE C,
                 B TYPE C.
    SELECTION-SCREEN END OF BLOCK B1.


*枠に囲い線をつける：WITH FRAME
    SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF BLOCK B2 WITH FRAME.
    PARAMETERS : C TYPE C,
                           D TYPE C.
    SELECTION-SCREEN END OF BLOCK B2.


* 枠に囲い線をつける：WITH FRAME      *枠の表題を付ける：TITEL
    SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF BLOCK B3 WITH FRAME TITLE TEXT-S01  .
    PARAMETERS : E TYPE C,
                           F TYPE C.
    SELECTION-SCREEN END OF BLOCK B3.
    
* 枠に囲い線をつける：WITH FRAME      *枠の表題を付ける：TITEL *線を引く：ULINE
      SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF BLOCK B4 WITH FRAME TITLE TEXT-S01.
      SELECTION-SCREEN ULINE.
      PARAMETERS : G TYPE C,
                             H TYPE C.
      SELECTION-SCREEN END OF BLOCK B4.

* 枠に囲い線をつける：WITH FRAME   *枠の表題を付ける：TITEL  *線を引く：ULINE  *文字を出力する：COMMENT
      SELECTION-SCREEN COMMENT  /10(13) TEXT-S02.

      SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF BLOCK B5 WITH FRAME TITLE TEXT-S01.
      SELECTION-SCREEN ULINE.
      PARAMETERS :I TYPE C,
                           J TYPE C.
      SELECTION-SCREEN END OF BLOCK B5.
      
      
  *二选一
SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF BLOCK BK2 WITH FRAME TITLE TEXT-T02.

   SELECTION-SCREEN  BEGIN OF LINE. ""设置同行

   PARAMETERS R_MALE   RADIOBUTTON GROUP GP1.
   SELECTION-SCREEN COMMENT (10) TEXT-T04 FOR FIELD R_MALE. ""T04里面设置选项文字
   SELECTION-SCREEN POSITION  20.

   PARAMETERS R_FEMALE  RADIOBUTTON GROUP GP1.
   SELECTION-SCREEN COMMENT (10) TEXT-T05 FOR FIELD R_FEMALE. ""T05里面设置选项文字
   SELECTION-SCREEN POSITION  20.
   SELECTION-SCREEN END OF LINE.

   SELECTION-SCREEN END OF BLOCK BK2.
   
   
   
   
   
      
